<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٥٣١٥ - عَبَّادُ بْنُ الْعَوَّامِ، عَنْ هِشَامٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ:</span> <span class="c3">{رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً، وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً}</span> <span class="c4">[البقرة: ٢٠١]</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي الدُّنْيَا الْعِلْمُ وَالْعِبَادَةُ , وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ الْجَنَّةُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>